who were coming from transplant had not achieved to CR going into the maintenance,

00:05:31.360 --> 00:05:32.200
uh,

00:05:32.200 --> 00:05:34.960
and had not achieved MRD negativity.

00:05:35.320 --> 00:05:36.100
And after,

00:05:36.100 --> 00:05:36.520
uh,

00:05:36.520 --> 00:05:37.060
going,

00:05:37.060 --> 00:05:37.520
uh,

00:05:37.520 --> 00:05:42.280
through teclistamab maintenance or during teclistamab maintenance with various follow-up,

00:05:42.460 --> 00:05:44.140
the best response was a hundred,

00:05:44.200 --> 00:05:44.740
um,

00:05:45.400 --> 00:05:50.780
close to a hundred percent overall response rate across all three arms with a hundred percent MRD negativity rate.

00:05:50.780 --> 00:05:55.700
So it's a notable deepening of response and MRD negativity rate in that post-transplant.

00:05:55.700 --> 00:05:57.540
So it's a notable deepening of response and MRD negativity rate in that post-transplant setting.

00:05:57.540 --> 00:05:58.040
Um,

