So I think there are a lot of,

00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:07.660
um,

00:06:07.660 --> 00:06:10.460
things we can glean from all of these studies so far.

00:06:10.460 --> 00:06:10.960
Uh,

00:06:10.960 --> 00:06:15.540
